<br>
Verant is putting these dumb drops out there, like range items that have high damage and low dealy...wtf? They are one of the last classes that wanna draw aggro, but yet their weapons are designed for it. I dont know about you guys, but I beleive if a good bow comes out, a Ranger should have first priority over it. Like the Nightmare Bow, nice bow...but it procs Shadow Vortex, which used to be a big taunt for SK tanks. Why? And ofcourse being one of the better bows and the coolest design, Rangers will want it, and should get it...but why the aggro proc?<br>
<br>
